{"tid":1811634,"cid":36,"subCid":0,"title":"有冇人做運動出汗皮膚會起粒粒同癢","createTime":"2020-01-04T23:30:48.000Z","updateTime":"2020-02-27T16:06:15.000Z","uid":344824,"like":0,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":11,"replies":[{"pid":"9af7d1505426ea98da243da78390dce786cb0553","tid":1811634,"uid":344824,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-01-04T23:30:48.000Z","msg":"如題,我由細到大都做開運動出汗好爽冇乜野<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 但係三個月前我有一次發夢被大量玻璃碎濺中入晒衫到 之後小弟立即番左屋企沖涼 第二日做gym一出汗皮膚就會起到一撻撻加有粒粒同埋好癢 但係啲汗乾晒大既半個鐘又冇事<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n而加又復發番仲勁過之前<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n有冇巴絲有試過醫唔醫到 同埋咩嚟<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2xm/dust.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"43433a9bf8985109542f03679e011a798fa127c9","tid":1811634,"uid":214635,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-01-04T23:32:16.000Z","msg":"疱疹2型 ，不過唔係生係J，扑野惹返黎<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5b762d3aea554daae549f4788a7e19a2928c3069","tid":1811634,"uid":344824,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"43433a9bf8985109542f03679e011a798fa127c9","tid":1811634,"uid":214635,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-01-04T23:32:16.000Z","msg":"疱疹2型 ，不過唔係生係J，扑野惹返黎<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-04T23:33:05.000Z","msg":"屌 咪嚇我<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0f619aa992e90eeca2e8964832b822b95907ea7c","tid":1811634,"uid":148053,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-04T23:36:28.000Z","msg":"普通敏感姐屌，我都有，吹撚到疱疹咁"},{"pid":"eb5d28f1973c46aa92d54d102117441f0e6460f6","tid"